snippet.title: Luckiest in the Megaverse [Demo Trailer]
snippet.description:
Test your luck in this cosmological clicker game where only luck matters. 
Play the Demo and add it to your WISHLIST on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2789760/The_Luckiest_in_the_Megaverse/
The Lucky Club awaits you.



Credits:
